# API Endpoints - Atlas AI Workouts Project
# Updated: 2025-08-30T00:00:00Z

## Workout Generation Endpoints

### POST /api/workouts/generate-simple
**Purpose**: Generate AI-powered workout based on client data and preferences
**Method**: POST
**Content-Type**: application/json
**Request Body**:
```typescript
{
  title: string,           // Workout name/title
  clientId: string,        // Client ID or 'guest'
  client: Client,          // Client object with full_name, goals, etc.
  duration: number,        // Workout duration in minutes
  intensity: string,       // 'light' | 'moderate' | 'intense'
  focus?: string,          // Focus area (optional)
  equipment?: string[],    // Available equipment array
  context?: any           // Training context object (optional)
}
```
**Response**:
```typescript
{
  success: boolean,
  workout: any,           // Generated workout object
  workoutId: string      // Unique workout identifier
}
```
